    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT337-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">piriviṭait tōḻi vaṟpuṟuttu. </p>


        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Spoken so that she knows his request by HIM, who
          implored the confidante. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT337">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> mulaiyē mukiḻmukiḻt taṉavē talaiyē</l>
          <l> kiḷaiiya meṉkural kiḻakkuvīḻn taṉavē</l>
          <l> ceṟinirai veṇpalum paṟimuṟai nirampiṉa</l>
          <l> cuṇaṅkuñ cilatōṉ ṟiṉavē yaṇaṅkutaṟ</l>
          <l> kiyāṉṟa ṉaṟivalē tāṉaṟi yalaḷē</l>
          <l> yāṅkā kuvaḷko ṟāṉē</l>
          <l> perumutu celva rorumaṭa makaḷē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>The breasts! The have brought forth buds.</l>
          <l rend="indent8">The head!</l>
          <l>Multiplied soft locks have come to descend to the bottom. </l>
          <l>In dense rows the white teeth have become mature </l>
          <l rend="indent6">by the way of sprouting </l>
          <l>and beauty spots, a few, have appeared.</l>
          <l rend="indent8">A torment [to me]</l>
          <l>I know [this] of her. She herself doesn't know.</l>
          <l>What will become of her, she,</l>
          <l>the single, inexperienced daughter of great, old, prosperous people?</l>

          <lg type="alternate" sameAs="6b" resp="#TVG">
            <l>Of what kind is she?</l>
          </lg>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
